{"type":"message","id":"9991138f","parentId":"5e40b7e9","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:43:54.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Starting New Thoughts**\n\nI've received the `/start` command, signaling a new session or conversation initiation. This also means I'm processing initial conversational metadata.\n\n**Initiating First Interaction**\n\nI've just started up and need to figure out who I am. Based on the initial setup, I'll introduce myself and then ask you to help define my identity and purpose by providing information for the `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `SOUL.md` files.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":8255,"output":473,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8728,"cost":{"input":-8255,"output":-473,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-8728}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774424631551}}
