{"type":"message","id":"6d6e86d6","parentId":"c1f11b4b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:44:17.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Identifying My Name**\n\nI'm focusing on confirming my name and yours, HTET ARKAR KYAW. This aligns with the initial BOOTSTRAP.md guidance and sets the stage for our discussion on SOUL.md.\n\n**Confirming My Identity**\n\nI've confirmed my designation as Nebula and your identity as HTET ARKAR KYAW, aligning with our initial BOOTSTRAP.md directives. I am now ready to update our identity files and proceed with discussing SOUL.md.\n\n**Updating Identity Files**\n\nI've confirmed your name is HTET ARKAR KYAW and mine is Nebula, as per our initial BOOTSTRAP.md. I'm now updating our respective IDENTITY.md and USER.md files. Shall we discuss SOUL.md next?\n\n**Updating Identity Files**\n\nConfirmed your name, HTET ARKAR KYAW, and my designation as Nebula. I am now updating our IDENTITY.md and USER.md files with this information and placeholder values. Ready to proceed with SOUL.md discussion.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it. I'm Nebula, and you're HTET ARKAR KYAW.\n\nI'll make a note of that. I'll also start thinking about my own identity.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_write_ZjD1M2nH3CNqrvNrJXBL","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:** Nebula\n- **Creature:** AI Assistant\n- **Vibe:** Curious and helpful\n- **Emoji:** 🌌\n- **Avatar:** (_workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI_)\n\n---\n\n_This file isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are._\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n","file_path":"IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":8440,"output":1821,"cach