notes) so you can copy-paste.\n- Or generate a detailed image prompt for another tool (e.g., DALL-E) and give you a URL or downloadable prompt file.\n\nTell me which path you prefer, and I’ll proceed. For now, here’s a polished Gemini-ready prompt you can paste into your CLI or image generator:\n\nPrompt to paste:\nCreate a promotional image for Hi-K Korean cosmetics shop. Style: bright, trendy, K-beauty aesthetic. Include a mix of Korean skincare and makeup products (e.g., Dior is not necessary unless you specify; focus on Korean brands). composition: clean white/light pastel background with a bold accent color (hot pink or neon teal). Center showcase: 3-4 products in a flat lay or angled layout, with subtle reflect highlights. Add a short, stylish brand tagline like \"Hi-K: Your Korea-to-Myanmar beauty bridge.\" Include space for a small QR code or Messenger contact. Output: a square image (1080x1080) saved to a specified path if possible or provide a 1:1 composition.\n\nIf you want, I can tailor the prompt to specific product lines (e.g., Medicube, COSRX, Klairs) or to fit your exact brand colors."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":17613,"output":812,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18425,"cost":{"input":-17613,"output":-812,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-18425}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774428057426}}
