{"type":"message","id":"3b2e348a","parentId":"2a65279d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T09:07:53.021Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ရပါတယ်၊ Gemini-based image generation လိုချင်တယ်ဆိုတာ ခ756 လက်ခံပြန်ပြောထားပေမယ့် ဒီအတိုင်း အော်ပရေတာမှာ gemini CLI ကို run လုပ်နိုင်တဲ့ environment မရှိလို့ direct image ကို မဖန်တီးနိုင်ပေ။ ဒါပေမယ့် သင့်အတွက် Gemini-ready prompts သေချာပြင်ထားပေးနိုင်ပါတယ်။ နောက်ပိုင်းမှာ သင့်ယုံကြည်ပြီး local machine ရှိ Gemini CLI ကို run လိုက်နိုင်မယ်ဆိုရင် အောက်ပါ prompt ကို copy-paste လုပ်ပြီး generate လုပ်ဖို့အဆင်သင့်ဖြစ်ပါပြီ။\n\n1) Gemini-ready image prompt (Hi-K – Korean cosmetics shop)\n- Command to run (copy-paste into Gemini CLI):\ngemini -p \"Create a promotional image for Hi-K Korean cosmetics shop. Style: bright, trendy, K-beauty aesthetic. Include 3-4 Korean skincare and makeup products. Background: clean white or light pastel with a bold accent color (hot pink or neon teal). Flat lay or angled composition with subtle reflections and soft shadows. Space for a QR code or Messenger contact. Tagline: 'Hi-K: Your Korea-to-Myanmar beauty bridge.' Output: square image 1080x1080. Save to ~/hi-k-promo.png if possible.\"\n\n- Image notes to tailor (optional):\n  - Focus brands: Medicube/COSRX/Etc. (if you want specific brands)\n  - Accent color: hot pink vs. neon teal\n  - Include a small placeholder for QR/Messenger icon\n\n2) Gemini-friendly image prompt (Hi-K product line variant)\n- Copy-paste this variant if you want another look:\ngemini -p \"Create a square promotional image for Hi-K Korean cosmetics shop. Style: bright, trendy, vibrant K-beauty. Feature 4-5 Korean skincare and makeup items in a flat lay. White background with pastel accents and a bold accent color. Include glossy highlights and shallow shadows. Reserve space for a QR code and 'Inbox us on Messenger' text. Tagline: 'Hi-K: Korea to Myanmar beauty bridge.' Output: 1080x1080.\"\n\n3) If you don’t have Gemini locally, I can generate a ready-to-upload