{"type":"message","id":"6be45189","parentId":"9d12ac2d","timestamp":"2026-03-25T12:12:05.221Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"39\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1677157143\",\n  \"sender\": \"Hi-K\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-25 12:12 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Hi-K (1677157143)\",\n  \"id\": \"1677157143\",\n  \"name\": \"Hi-K\",\n  \"username\": \"lioptae\"\n}\n```\n\n\"Hi OpenClaw, I want to create a new skill called draft_facebook_post. This skill should use the data I trained you on (Myan-Poh and Hi-K) to generate a Facebook post content (text) and an image description. The image description should be used to generate an image using DALL-E.\""}],"timestamp":1774440725216}}
