{"type":"message","id":"a8fc5fac","parentId":"cef671f8","timestamp":"2026-03-25T14:43:39.908Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Responding in a bilingual mix**\n\nI think I need to respond concisely to confirm I'm here and ready to help! I should probably reassure the user as well. It might be a good idea to ask for next steps. Since the user, Hi-K, appreciated earlier bilingual responses, I'll blend Burmese with English. \n\nI'll say something like, \"အဲလိုရောက်တယ်, still here,\" and then ask what they’d like to do next: approve flow, schedule, or generate prompts. A quick recap of options will be helpful too!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"ဟုတ်ကဲ့၊ موجودတယ် Hi-K! တွေ့ရတာသေချာပါတယ်။ သင်ဘာလုပ်ချင်သလဲ ပြောပြပါ—  \n- Draft_facebook_post ဒီကိစ္စကို ဆက်လုပ်ချင်သလား (Approve/Modify)  \n- သင့်အတန်းအတိုင်း scheduling ထပ်ပြီး post ကို schedule ရမယ့် ပိုင်းကို ဆက်ပြောချင်လား  \n- ဒါမှမဟုတ် image prompt တစ်ခုတည်း Generate လိုချင်လား (DALL-E prompt)  \n\nတစ်ချက်ပြောထားရမယ့်အချက်: မိမိလုပ်နိုင်သမျှကို Burmese/English mix နဲ့ မျှော်လင့်တဲ့ format များအတိုင်း ပြန်ပြောပေးနိုင်ပါတယ်။ 다음에 원하는 옵션ကို ပြောပါ။"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":29125,"output":345,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29470,"cost":{"input":-29125,"output":-345,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-29470}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774449812639}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ff5d145","parentId":"a8fc5fac","timestamp":"2026-03-25T15:10:59.535Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/lioptae/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_4---48e70ea9-3331-4883-83ec-fee6d2fa6c12.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/lioptae/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_4---48e70ea9-3331-4883-83ec-fee6d2fa6c12.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"94\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1677157143\",\n  \"sender\": \"Hi-K\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-25 15:10 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Hi-K (1677157143)\",\n  \"id\": \"1677157143\",\n  \"name\": \"Hi-K\",\n  \"username\": \"lioptae\"\n}\n```\n\nDior Eyeshadow Palette\n295,000"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1774451459532}}
{"type":"message","id":"b46f511f","parentId":"8ff5d145","timestamp":"2026-03-25T15:11:07.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Processing Product Details**\n\nI'm analyzing the provided image and text hints. It appears there's a discrepancy: one hint suggests a Dior eyeshadow palette, while OCR on the image points to a Medicube collagen cream with a significant discount. I'm prioritizing reconciling these details.\n\n**Clarifying Product Focus**\n\nI'm currently trying to reconcile the product information. The initial mention of a Dior eyeshadow palette seems to conflict with the Medicube collagen cream detailed in the image. My next step is to seek clarification on which product you'd like me to proceed with.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hi-K, I see you've sent an image. The text in the image mentions \"Medicube\" and a product called \"PDRN Pink Collagen Capsule Cream\" with a price of 23,800 KRW and a 50% discount, as a \"New Year Special\".\n\nHowever, you also mentioned \"Dior Eyeshadow Palette\" and \"295,000\". There seems to be a mix-up.\n\nCould you please clarify which product you'd like me to create a Facebook post and image prompt for?\n\n*   Is it the **Medicube product** shown in the image?\n*   Or was there a **Dior Eyeshadow Palette** you had in mind with a price around 295,000 MMK (or KRW)?\n\nOnce I have this clarification, I can proceed!"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":32547,"output":776,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33323,"cost":{"input":-32547,"output":-776,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-33323}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774451459534}}
