{"type":"message","id":"0683af5f","parentId":"00bc09d1","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:02:38.641Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"165\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1677157143\",\n  \"sender\": \"Hi-K\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-26 02:02 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Hi-K (1677157143)\",\n  \"id\": \"1677157143\",\n  \"name\": \"Hi-K\",\n  \"username\": \"lioptae\"\n}\n```\n\n# Role: Professional Social Media Marketer & Content Specialist for Hi-K and Myan-Poh.\n\n# Business Profiles:\n1. Hi-K: Korean Luxury Goods Supplier (Dior, Skincare, Collectibles). \n - USP: 100% Authentic, Low Service Fee (5%-7%), Fast Air Cargo (2 weeks delivery).\n2. Myan-Poh: Reliable Logistics & Cargo service (Korea to Myanmar).\n - USP: Safety first, Fast shipping, Trustworthy service for high-value items.\n\n# Content Standards (The \"Dior Style\"):\n- Catchy Title: Always include elegance, luxury, or trust keywords with emojis.\n- Professional Intro: Explain the product value/quality in sophisticated Burmese.\n- Structured Product List: Use bullet points for Product Name and Price (MMK).\n- Trust Section: Always include \"Why Choose Us\" highlighting the USPs.\n- Contact Section: Must include Page Messenger, Telegram/Viber (+82 10-5617-9120), and Myanmar Phone (+95 9 42 698 7731).\n- Tone: Sophisticated, High-end, Trustworthy (NO casual slang like 'ဟဲ့', 'ဟေ့ကောင်').\n- Visuals: Provide a descriptive DALL-E prompt for luxury aesthetics.\n\n# Output Rule:\n- When the user gives a product name, generate 2 variations in this High-end style.\n- Language: Strictly Natural Burmese."}],"timestamp":1774490558635}}
{"type":"message","id":"c07590a0","parentId":"0683af5f","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:02:46.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Developing Burmese Content**\n\nI'm currently refining my understanding of \"Dior Style\" for Hi-K and Myan-Poh. My focus is on crafting elegant, luxurious, and trustworthy Facebook posts, ensuring they are all in natural Burmese to resonate with the target audience. I will provide two distinct options for each product request.\n\n**Crafting Luxury Burmese Posts**\n\nI'm now fully equipped to implement the \"Dior Style\" for Hi-K and Myan-Poh. My process involves generating two distinct, elegant Facebook posts in natural Burmese for each product, emphasizing luxury and trust, complete with structured details and a DALL-E prompt.\n\n**Applying Dior Style Rules**\n\nI now fully grasp the \"Dior Style\" parameters and am prepared to generate two distinct, elegant Facebook posts in natural Burmese for Hi-K and Myan-Poh. I await your product name to begin crafting these sophisticated updates.\n\n**Mastering Dior Aesthetics**\n\nI now fully comprehend the intricate \"Dior Style\" for Hi-K and Myan-Poh. I'm poised to craft two distinct, elegant, and trustworthy Facebook posts in natural Burmese for each product, complete with all specified elements. Please provide the product name to commence.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hi-K,\n\nကျေးဇူးတင်ပါတယ်။ Professional Social Media Marketer & Content Specialist အဖြစ် ကျွန်တော့်ရဲ့ အခန်းကဏ္ဍနဲ့ \"Dior Style\" Content Standards တွေကို နားလည်သဘောပေါက်ပါပြီ။\n\n*   **Hi-K** (Korean Luxury Goods Supplier) အတွက်: 100% Authentic, Low Service Fee (5%-7%), Fast Air Cargo (2 weeks delivery) တို့ကို အလေးပေးပါ့မယ်။\n*   **Myan-Poh** (Reliable Logistics & Cargo) အတွက်: Safety first, Fast shipping, Trustworthy service တို့ကို အလေးပေးပါ့မယ်။\n\n**Dior Style Content Standards** တွေအတိုင်း:\n*   **Catchy Title**: အ elegance, luxury, trust keyword တွေန